product_name: DeLorme Minnesota Atlas and Gazetteer - 3rd Edition
long_description: Detailed maps of the entire state of Minnesota include back roads, backwater lakes and streams and campgrounds. DeLorme Publishing; copyright 2001. Map scale is 1:190,000 with a contour interval of 20 meters (approximately 66 feet). Each pages covers 28.6 x 43.2 miles. Ideal for outdoor recreation, reference, business, engineering and emergency services; GPS compatible. Also covers state forest lands, state wildlife management areas; national waterfowl production areas are highlighted in color. Updated park, campground and rail name information.
short_description: Detailed maps of the entire state of Minnesota include back roads, backwater lakes and streams and campgrounds.
